"title": "5044: names, giving of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5044: names, giving of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture contains many examples of the naming of people and places. Personal names, usually given at birth by parents, were sometimes changed at a later date.</p>\n<h2>Names may reflect personal experiences</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:51-Gen41:52\">GEN 41:51–41:52</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen29:31-Gen29:35\">GEN 29:31–29:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:6-Gen30:8\">GEN 30:6–30:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:18-Gen30:20\">GEN 30:18–30:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen30:23-Gen30:24\">GEN 30:23–30:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:18\">GEN 35:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:10\">EXO 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod2:21-Exod2:22\">EXO 2:21–2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:3-Exod18:4\">EXO 18:3–18:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:20\">1SA 1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr4:9\">1CH 4:9</a></p>\n<h2>Names may reflect national experiences</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam4:21\">1SA 4:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen10:25\">GEN 10:25</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr1:19\">1CH 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:3-Isa8:4\">ISA 8:3–8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos1:2-Hos1:11\">HOS 1:2–1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Names may indicate future destiny</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:21\">MAT 1:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:31-Luke1:33\">LUK 1:31–1:33</a></p>\n<h2>The giving of a name reflects the authority of the giver</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:5-Gen1:10\">GEN 1:5–1:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:19-Gen2:20\">GEN 2:19–2:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:23\">GEN 2:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:18\">GEN 35:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:34\">2KI 23:34</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr36:4\">2CH 36:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs24:17\">2KI 24:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:62-Luke1:63\">LUK 1:62–1:63</a></p>\n<h2>The changing of names</h2>\n<h3>On divine instruction</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:3-Gen17:8\">GEN 17:3–17:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:15-Gen17:16\">GEN 17:15–17:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:9-Gen35:10\">GEN 35:9–35:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:42\">JHN 1:42</a></p>\n<h3>In relation to salvation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:2\">ISA 62:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:15\">ISA 65:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:17\">REV 2:17</a></p>\n<h3>In the light of past experience</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:32\">JDG 6:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth1:20\">RUT 1:20</a></p>\n<h3>In the future</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:3\">ZEC 8:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:26\">ISA 1:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:5\">ISA 44:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa58:12\">ISA 58:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:4\">ISA 62:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa62:12\">ISA 62:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:32\">JER 7:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:3-Jer20:6\">JER 20:3–20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal1:4\">MAL 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>In a new culture</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen41:45\">GEN 41:45</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan1:7\">DAN 1:7</a></p>\n<h3>The instance of Paul</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts13:9\">ACT 13:9</a> <em>The occasion of and reason for the change from “Saul” to “Paul” are not clear.</em></p>\n<h2>Place-names may reflect events or experiences</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:8-Gen11:9\">GEN 11:8–11:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen16:13-Gen16:14\">GEN 16:13–16:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:21-Gen19:22\">GEN 19:21–19:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen21:31\">GEN 21:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen26:32-Gen26:33\">GEN 26:32–26:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:18-Gen28:19\">GEN 28:18–28:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen31:45-Gen31:50\">GEN 31:45–31:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:1-Gen32:2\">GEN 32:1–32:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen32:30\">GEN 32:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen33:17\">GEN 33:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:7-Gen35:8\">GEN 35:7–35:8</a></p>",
